snippet: Serena Williams will be joined by big sister Venus in the women's field for the BNP Paribas Open in March, a year after Serena returned to the desert tournament in an end to her 14-year boycott....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams will be joined by big sister Venus in the women's field for the BNP Paribas Open in March, a year after Serena returned to the desert tournament in an end to her 14-year boycott.

headline.print_headline: Serena and Venus Williams to Compete at Indian Wells Tourney
headline.main: Serena and Venus Williams to Compete at Indian Wells Tourney
